---
import Headline from "./Headline.astro";

---

<section>
    <article class="flow">
        <Headline backgroundcolor="gray scale 8" text="CONTACT"/>
        <h2>Ready To Talk?</h2>
        <p>Posuere sollicitudin aliquam ultrices sagittis orci a scelerisque. Massa placerat duis ultricies lacus sed turpis. Pellentesque  pellentesque habitant morbi tristique.</p>
        <label>
            <input type="email" id="mail" name="mail" placeholder="Your mail address">
            <input type="submit" id="submitbtn" name="mail" value="Send Meassage">
        </label>
    </article>
    <article>

    </article>
</section>

<style>

    section{
        background-color: var(--primary-color-3-default);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl, 1rem);
        border-radius: 1rem;
        padding-inline: var(--space-xl);
        padding-block: var(--space-3xl, 1rem);
    }

    h2, p{
        color: var(--gray-scale-05);
    }

    label{
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    #mail{
        background-color: var(--gray-scale-05);
        padding-block: var(--space-s);
        padding-inline: var(--space-m);
        border-radius: 2rem;

    }

    #submitbtn{
        background-color: var(--primary-color-2-default);
        color: var(--gray-scale-05);
        padding-block: var(--space-s);
        padding-inline: var(--space-m);
        border-radius: 2rem;
    }

</style>